summary: An ordinance approving and confirming the assessment and assessment roll of Local Improvement District No. 5587 for the improvement of The Alley in Block 9, Byron Addition, being the alley between Rainier Avenue and Wetmore Avenue, from Walden Street to Byron Street; by paving and otherwise improving the same; under Ordinance No. 73387, and levying and assessing the amounts thereof against the several lots, tracts, parcels of land and other property as shown on said roll, establishing a Local Improvement Fund.
